{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"0946e365-ea8e-4c9e-9719-0373ba7344a5","content":"In .NET MAUI, the `Application`-level `OnStart`/`OnSleep`/`OnResume` overrides are replaced by **Window lifecycle events**. Override `CreateWindow` in your `App` class and hook into the window events:\n\n```csharp\npublic partial class App : Application\n{\n    protected override Window CreateWindow(IActivationState? activationState)\n    {\n        var window = base.CreateWindow(activationState);\n\n        window.Created += (s, e) => { /* OnStart equivalent */ };\n        window.Stopped += (s, e) => { /* OnSleep equivalent */ };\n        window.Resumed += (s, e) => { /* OnResume equivalent */ };\n\n        return window;\n    }\n}\n```\n\nAlternatively, subclass `Window` and override `OnCreated()`, `OnStopped()`, and `OnResumed()` directly.\n\nFor platform-specific hooks, use `ConfigureLifecycleEvents` in `MauiProgram.cs`.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"d35d17b8-df85-4ffa-814a-e9a0f088ee19","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about migrating lifecycle methods from Xamarin.Forms to .NET MAUI. This is a straightforward knowledge question about the MAUI lifecycle API.\n\nIn Xamarin.Forms, you'd override `OnStart`, `OnSleep`, and `OnResume` in your `Application` subclass.\n\nIn .NET MAUI, the lifecycle model changed. Instead of overriding those methods directly, you use the `Window` lifecycle events or the `ILifecycleBuilder` in `MauiProgram.cs`. Specifically:\n\n1. You can override `CreateWindow` in your `App` class and subscribe to window events like `Created`, `Resumed`, `Stopped`, `Destroying`, etc.\n\n\n2. Alternatively, you can configure platform-specific lifecycle events through `ConfigureLifecycleEvents` in `MauiProgram.cs`, or subclass `Window` and override the corresponding lifecycle methods. The direct mapping is `OnStart` → `Window.Created`, `OnSleep` → `Window.Stopped`, and `OnResume` → `Window.Resumed`.","outputTokens":548,"requestId":"482C:386B3C:53E193C:5C0B63A:69F3FB7E"},"id":"f81157fd-5699-498d-81c5-b0c0253bdb4b","timestamp":"2026-05-01T01:02:00.755Z","parentId":"8192a91a-ad7d-43af-8831-e100d6db28cb"}
